  "texts": [
    "By consolidating insights from food science, sensory neuroscience, and computational modeling, the paper outlines both the capabilities and the limitations of AI in this domain.",
    "This perspective helps clarify how AI can support the modeling of human sensory responses, particularly by bridging the gap between subjective perception and objective computational prediction.",
    "Through this synthesis, the review offers a reference point for researchers and practitioners seeking to better understand the role of AI in sensory science and to apply these tools in practical contexts such as flavor optimization, product customization, and health-related interventions.",
    "To ensure that AI can fulfill its potential in advancing olfactory and gustatory applications, several critical areas require further attention.",
    "Future research should prioritize the development of diverse and representative datasets that capture global variation in sensory experiences."
  ],
